description: This top 15% Gaston purrs with a rating of 26, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 130, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
